{
    "version": 2,
    "mode": "web-ga-ads",
    "directives": {
        "default-src": ["'self'"],
        "script-src": [
            "'self'",
            "'unsafe-inline'",
            "https://www.googletagmanager.com",
            "https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com"
        ],
        "style-src": ["'self'", "'unsafe-inline'"],
        "img-src": [
            "'self'",
            "data:",
            "blob:",
            "https://www.google-analytics.com",
            "https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com",
            "https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net",
            "https://tpc.googlesyndication.com"
        ],
        "font-src": ["'self'", "data:"],
        "connect-src": [
            "'self'",
            "https://www.google-analytics.com",
            "https://region1.analytics.google.com",
            "https://www.googletagmanager.com",
            "https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com",
            "https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net"
        ],
        "frame-src": [
            "https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net",
            "https://tpc.googlesyndication.com",
            "https://adservice.google.com"
        ],
        "worker-src": ["'self'", "blob:"],
        "child-src": ["'none'"],
        "frame-ancestors": ["'none'"],
        "object-src": ["'none'"],
        "base-uri": ["'none'"],
        "form-action": ["'self'"],
        "upgrade-insecure-requests": []
    },
    "notes": [
        "Mengizinkan GA/gtag & AdSense. Inline script diperlukan untuk snippet gtag(), hence 'unsafe-inline'.",
        "Jika ingin tanpa 'unsafe-inline', gunakan nonce/hash dan terapkan ke tag <script> inline.",
        "frame-ancestors tetap 'none' agar situs tidak bisa di-embed pihak lain."
    ]
}
